msgid "[![launch ImageJ.JS](https://ij.imjoy.io/assets/badge/open-in-imagej-js-badge.svg)](https://ij.imjoy.io/?open=https://github.com/bioimagebook/practical-data/blob/main/images/lost_dimensions.tif)"
